 joining more than two tables :-
------------------------------------------

 =>  if no of tables increaes no of join conditions also increases 
 =>  To join N tables N-1 join conditions required 
 =>  For ex to join 4 tables 3  join conditions  required

  SELECT columns
  FROM tab1 
  INNER JOIN tab2
  ON join cond1
  INNER JOIN tab3
  ON join cond2
  INNER JOIN tab4
  ON join cond3
