 => display     ename	dname	city	state	country_name   ?
                      ----------                -----------   ----------------------        -----------------------
                         emp                    dept        locations                  countries

    SELECT e.ename,
                   d.department_name,
                   l.city,l.state,
                   c.country_name 
   FROM     employees e 
   INNER JOIN departments d
   ON e.deptid = d.deptid
   INNER JOIN locations l
   ON d.locid = l.locid
   INNER JOIN countries c
   ON l.country_id = c.country_id 

 
 OUTER JOIN :- 
 ----------------------

 => equi join returns only matching records but will not return unmatched records
 => to display unmatched records  also perform outer join
 => outer join is 3 types 

1 left outer join
2 right outer join
3 full outer join

Ex :-

     EMP					DEPT
     empno	   ename	  sal	deptno		deptno	dname		loc
      1	    A	  3000	10		10	ACCOUNTS	NEW YORK
      2	   B	  4000	20		20	RESEARCH	??
      3	   C	  5000	30		30	SALES		?
      4	   D	  3000	20		40	OPERATIONS	? => unmatched from dept
      5	   E	  4000	10
      6	   F	  2000	NULL => unmatched from emp
 
 
 emp.deptno = dept.deptno   => good   => 9 comparisons

 dept.deptno = emp.deptno  => bad   => 20 comparisons

